                           donor; two initial lines of Gospel chapters and other minor texts;
                           chapter numbers and the word mǝʿǝraf; parts of the Canon tables; elements
                           of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals within the
                           text.
 
 The incipits of Texts I-V are written alternately in red
